FBIS4-39009 "drsov108_b_94023" FBIS-SOV-94-108 Daily Report 3 Jun 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Military Issues New Border Guard Control Center Inaugurated New Border Guard Control Center Inaugurated PM0306143594 Moscow ROSSIYSKIYE VESTI in Russian 3 Jun 94 p 1 PM0306143594 Moscow ROSSIYSKIYE VESTI Russian BFN [Unattributed untitled report under the "At A Glance" rubric] [Text] The Russian Border Guards Central Command Post, which was set up on the initiative of Colonel General Andrey Nikolayev, commander in chief of the [border guard] troops, has embarked on duty. The post was set up with with a view to ensuring quality organization and operational command and control of the border guards. Shifts will be on duty around the clock.
